{"tid":658223,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【完勝Siri?】Google Assistant 大幅進化 可自動致電店鋪進行預約","createTime":"2018-05-08T19:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T12:49:54.000Z","uid":97606,"like":4,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"007c077da90f70e5934ade9867c05f164bb69095","tid":658223,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:17:19.000Z","msg":"Google Assistant 全面應用了 Google 的人工智能技術，在 I/O 大會上，其中一個得到重點介紹的部分就是這個智能語音助理，在更強勁的人工智能協助下，Google Assistant 也將加入更多功能。<br />\n<br />\n除了更自然的互動之外，Google Assistant 可以做到的功能也有所增加，其中 Google Duplex 技術將會應用到 Assistant 之中，除了可以理解更複雜的句子外，亦甚至可以作出相當自然的回應。在示範中，Google 甚至在測試一個功能，<span style=\"color: red;\">當用家想預約服務但店鋪沒有提供網上預約服務，Assistant 可以協助用家致電預約，用自然的對話與店鋪透過電話溝通，猶如真人祕書</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Screen-Shot-2018-05-09-at-2.24.29-AM-1280x709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2FScreen-Shot-2018-05-09-at-2.24.29-AM-1280x709.jpg&h=dbc0a063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細技術內容和電話對話錄音: <a href=\"https://ai.googleblog.com/2018/05/duplex-ai-system-for-natural-conversation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fai.googleblog.com%2F2018%2F05%2Fduplex-ai-system-for-natural-conversation.html&d=Bz9miVcwoXDXnofmbv%2BrrKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ea5b86eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://ai.googleblog.com/2018/05/duplex-ai-system-for-natural-conversation.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">擺到明就係搵演員做戲扮嘢啦, 如果做到呢個程度Turing test都pass到啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過就算真係俾google開發到呢個功能, 咪又係唔識講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想追Siri仲要用多幾十年呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 用siri好過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : google好撚勁!"},{"pid":"f5f54c287685ba8e1e86f2d948e596fc7f2125ca","tid":658223,"uid":171273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:29:00.000Z","msg":"Siri不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a63cbfdbed8057f36a3653e56a2b5367881ed9","tid":658223,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"f5f54c287685ba8e1e86f2d948e596fc7f2125ca","tid":658223,"uid":171273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:29:00.000Z","msg":"Siri不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:43:51.000Z","msg":"我日日用喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0763d11e453e9ad21c716eda86c07094b5678c","tid":658223,"uid":11598,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"92a63cbfdbed8057f36a3653e56a2b5367881ed9","tid":658223,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"f5f54c287685ba8e1e86f2d948e596fc7f2125ca","tid":658223,"uid":171273,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:29:00.000Z","msg":"Siri不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:43:51.000Z","msg":"我日日用喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018